"Individual applications for this competition are not allowed, as it is a subcategory of the main Enterprise of the Year competition", explains Karel Goldman of Bison & Rose.
Police made arrests during a public auction at the Agricultural Fund building in Pilsen
The anti-corruption police made several arrests in the building of the Agricultural Fund in the last days.
Detectives handcuffed a local media businessman and real estate developer Luboš G.
